Package cpsc2150.extendedConnectX.models

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IGameBoard
    An interface representing a 2D game board where (0,0) is the bottom left of the board.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbsGameBoard
    The abstract class AbsGameBoard implements the IGameBoard interface and provides a default implementation for the toString method by calling primary methods from the interface.
    BoardPosition
    This class will be used to keep track of an individual cell for a board.
    GameBoard
    This class keeps track of an individual cell on a game board thus representing the game board
    GameBoardMem
    A GameBoardMem represents a game board that is stored in memory.
